column2: SELECT  ap.apstar_id, ap.apogee_id, ap.glon, ap.glat, ap.ra, ap.dec, ao.pmra, ao.pmdec, ao.pmra_err, ao.pmdec_err, ast.teff, ast.logg, ap.vhelio_avg, ap.verr, ap.snr, ast.m_h, ast.m_h_err, ast.alpha_m, ast.alpha_m_err, ast.fparam_alpha_m, ast.fe_h, ast.fe_h_err, ast.mg_fe, ast.mg_fe_err, ast.si_fe, ast.si_fe_err, ast.felem_fe_h, ast.felem_mg_m, ast.felem_si_m into myDB.apogeeparam4 FROM dbo.aspcapStar as ast   JOIN dbo.apogeestar as ap ON (ap.apogee_id = ast.apogee_id)   JOIN dbo.apogeeObject as ao ON (ao.apogee_id = ast.apogee_id)
